file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
components:
  schemas:
    Department:
      type: object
      properties:
        supervisor:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Person"
        manager:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Person"

    Company:
      type: object
      properties:
        owner:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Person"
        employee:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Person"

    Person:
      type: object
      properties:
        home_address:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Address"

    Address:
      type: object
      properties:
        eircode:
          type: string
